'''2017年美國總統就職典禮'''，官方名稱為'''第58屆美國總統就職典禮'''（{{lang-en|the 58th Presidential Inauguration}}），也稱為'''當勞·覃普總統就職典禮'''，為[[美國總統列表|第45任]][[美國總統|美國總統]][[當勞·特朗普|當勞·覃普]]於2017年1月20日週五舉行的[[美國總統就職典禮|就職典禮]]，標誌著總統[[當勞·特朗普|當勞·覃普]]與副總統[[麥克·彭斯|麥克·彭斯]]領導的共和黨政府4年任期的开始。基于宣誓仪式上重点强调的“宪法制度的美式独特表达”，活动定题为“独特美国人”<ref name="theme">{{cite web |url=https://www.inaugural.senate.gov/imo/media/doc/Entire%20Program.pdf |title=Entire Program |accessdate=2017-01-18 |publisher=Joint Congressional Inauguration Committee |archive-date=2017-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120232548/https://www.inaugural.senate.gov/imo/media/doc/Entire%20Program.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，通过美国人“团结在恒久共和国的背后”的例子，展现权力的和平交接<ref name="theme"/>。2017年1月17日到21日，华盛顿特区举办了音乐会、宣誓仪式、午宴、游行、{{le|美国总统就职舞会|United States presidential inaugural balls|就职舞会}}、各宗教派别就职祷告仪式等就职活动。

典礼上，[[美国首席大法官|首席法官]][[约翰·罗伯茨|约翰·罗伯茨]]监督覃普宣誓，副总统彭斯则由[[美国最高法院大法官|最高法院大法官]][[克拉伦斯·托马斯|克拉伦斯·托马斯]]监督宣誓<ref>{{cite news |last=Staff |first=Writer |url=http://www.wpsdlocal6.com/story/34259109/vp-pence-to-be-sworn-in-by-clarence-thomas |title=VP Pence to be sworn in by Clarence Thomas |work=WPSD-TV |agency=Associated Press |date=2017-01-13 |accessdate=2017-01-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170115154626/http://www.wpsdlocal6.com/story/34259109/vp-pence-to-be-sworn-in-by-clarence-thomas |archivedate=2017-01-15 }}</ref>。覃普宣誓时左手按住他母親送贈的《圣经》和[[林肯圣经|林肯《圣经》]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/2017/01/17/510252058/trump-will-be-sworn-in-with-same-bible-as-lincoln-and-obama|title=Trump Will Be Sworn In With Same Bible As Lincoln And Obama|accessdate=2017-01-19|publisher=NPR|archive-date=2017-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118161759/http://www.npr.org/2017/01/17/510252058/trump-will-be-sworn-in-with-same-bible-as-lincoln-and-obama|dead-url=no}}</ref>。典礼伴随着美国和其他国家的抗议活动。

==背景==
就职典礼标志着{{le|唐纳德·特朗普总统过渡期|Presidential transition of Donald Trump}}正式结束。他于2016年11月8日赢得[[2016年美国总统选举|总统选举]]，成为当选总统<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/09/us/politics/hillary-clinton-donald-trump-president.html |title=Donald Trump Is Elected President in Stunning Repudiation of the Establishment |publisher=New York Times |accessdate=2017-01-21 |date=2016-11-09 |author=Flegenheimer, Matt |archive-date=2018-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225140519/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/11/09/us/politics/hillary-clinton-donald-trump-president.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。特朗普和他的竞选伙伴迈克·彭斯于2016年12月19日由[[美国选举人团|选举人团]]正式选举产生<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/dec/19/electoral-college-votes-donald-trump-electors|title=Electoral college formally elects Donald Trump as president|last=Jacobs|first=Ben|date=2016-12-19|newspaper=The Guardian|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|access-date=2016-12-19|archive-date=2016-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161219234640/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/dec/19/electoral-college-votes-donald-trump-electors|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/19/us/politics/electoral-college-vote.html|title=Donald Trump Completes Final Lap, Electoral College, to White House|last=The New York Times|date=2016-12-19|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-12-19|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121014733/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/19/us/politics/electoral-college-vote.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。胜选结果于2017年1月16日由[[美国国会联席会议|国会联席会议]]投票认可<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/trump-electoral-college-vote-certified-by-congress/|title=Congress certifies Trump's election victory|access-date=2017-01-16|archive-date=2017-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170108163749/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/trump-electoral-college-vote-certified-by-congress/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。就职后，特朗普成为首个没有任何军事或政府工作经验的当选总统<ref name="guardian">{{cite web |url=https://guardian.ng/features/weekend/america-stands-still-for-trump/ |title=America stands still for Trump |publisher=The Guardian |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-20 |author=Nwakunor, Gregory |archive-date=2017-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170122165521/http://guardian.ng/features/weekend/america-stands-still-for-trump/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，也是最年长和最富有的总统<ref name="guardian"/>。妻子[[梅拉尼娅·特朗普|梅拉尼娅]]成为继1825年成为总统的[[约翰·昆西·亚当斯|约翰·昆西·亚当斯]]夫人{{le|路易莎·亚当斯|Louisa Adams}}后第二位在国外出生的美國第一夫人<ref>{{cite book|last1=Harris|first1=Bill|last2=Ross|first2=Laura|date=2009-03-04|title=The First Ladies Fact Book: Revised and Updated! The Childhoods, Courtships, Marriages, Campaigns, Accomplishments, and Legacies of Every First Lady from Martha Washington to Michelle Obama|url=https://books.google.com/?id=KpRfLDnY44gC&pg=PT233&dq=louisa+adams+citizenship#v=onepage&q=louisa%20adams%20citizenship&f=false|publisher=Black Dog & Leventhal Publishers|isbn=1579128092}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.history.com/topics/first-ladies/louisa-adams|title=Louisa Adams - First Ladies|publisher=History.com|accessdate=2016-11-19|archive-date=2016-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161026221215/http://www.history.com/topics/first-ladies/louisa-adams|dead-url=no}}</ref>。迈克·彭斯成为自1968年[[理查德·尼克松|理查德·尼克松]]的伙伴[[斯皮罗·阿格纽|斯皮罗·阿格纽]]以来，第一位当选副总统的在任州长。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/15/politics/mike-pence-facts-donald-trump-vice-president-us-election/ |title=Mike Pence has a place in history |publisher=CNN |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2016-07-15 |author=Holland, Keating |archive-date=2018-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180203130016/http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/15/politics/mike-pence-facts-donald-trump-vice-president-us-election/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 規劃 ==
本次就職典禮主要由2個委員會策劃：[[美國國會就職典禮聯席委員會|美國國會就職典禮聯席委員會]]與2017年總統就職委員會。早在11月8日正式投票日前，联席委员会于9月21日便开始搭建就职典礼舞台<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.salon.com/2016/09/21/construction-begins-on-presidential-inauguration-platform/ |title=Construction begins on presidential inauguration platform |publisher=Salon |agency=Associated Press |author=Jalonick, Mary Clare |date=2016-09-21 |access-date=2017-01-17 |archive-date=2017-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118222238/http://www.salon.com/2016/09/21/construction-begins-on-presidential-inauguration-platform/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

负责策划当选总统特朗普和当选副总统彭斯宣誓就职仪式的联席委员会成员有联邦参议员肯塔基州[[米奇·麦康奈尔|米奇·麦康奈尔]]、密苏里州[[罗伊·布伦特|罗伊·布伦特]]（委员会主席）、纽约州[[查克·舒默|查克·舒默]]和联邦众议员威斯康辛州[[保罗·莱恩|保罗·莱恩]]、加利福尼亚州[[凯文·麦卡锡|凯文·麦卡锡]]和[[南希·佩洛西|南希·佩洛西]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.inaugural.senate.gov/about/past-committees |title=The 58th Inaugural Committee |accessdate=2017-01-17 |publisher=Joint Congressional Inauguration Committee |archive-date=2017-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120034439/https://www.inaugural.senate.gov/about/past-committees/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{le|美国参议院规则和行政委员会|U.S. Senate Committee on Rules and Administration}}负责监察。

联席委员会选定的就职典礼主题“独特美国人”（{{lang|en|Uniquely American}}）强调就职典礼是“我国宪法制度的美式独特展现”<ref name="theme"/>。主题也强调权力[[美国总统过渡|和平过渡]]，美国人“在恒久共和国的背后团结”<ref name="theme"/>。主题引用了特朗普的竞选口号“让美国再次强大”，这也是就职演讲的主题之一。

2015年12月21日，就职典礼委员会公布1月20日就职典礼日程表<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.58pic2017.org/press-releases/presidential-inaugural-committee-pic-unveils-inaugural-schedule-of-events |title=Presidential Inaugural Committee (PIC) Unveils Inaugural Schedule of Events |publisher=58th Presidential Inauguration Committee |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2016-12-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170119211525/https://www.58pic2017.org/press-releases/presidential-inaugural-committee-pic-unveils-inaugural-schedule-of-events |archivedate=2017-01-19 }}</ref>。{{le|首都地区联合特遣队|Joint Task Force National Capital Region}}负责协调就职典礼的军事支援，提供[[军事组织|军乐队]]、[[仪仗队|仪仗队]]、[[护旗队|护旗队]]、门卫兵、枪支和[[礼炮|礼炮]]<ref>{{cite web|title=On the road to the 58th U.S. Presidential Inauguration|url=https://www.army.mil/article/175648/on_the_road_to_the_58th_us_presidential_inauguration|website=www.army.mil|publisher=United States Army|accessdate=2016-12-23|date=2016-09-23|archive-date=2016-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223135419/https://www.army.mil/article/175648/on_the_road_to_the_58th_us_presidential_inauguration|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

而2017年总统就职委员会<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.58pic2017.org/|title=The 58th Presidential Inauguration|website=www.58pic2017.org|access-date=2016-12-19|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220080123/https://www.58pic2017.org/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>则组织音乐会、游行、舞会和祈祷仪式等其他与就职典礼相关的活动，受当选正副总统主管。委员会主席{{le|小托马斯·J·巴拉克|Thomas J. Barrack Jr.}}是[[房地产|房地产]]投资者、{{le|柯罗尼资本|Colony NorthStar}}主席兼[[首席执行官|首席执行官]]。{{le|刘易斯·艾森伯格|Lewis M. Eisenberg}}和罗伊·贝利（{{lang|en|Roy Bailey}}）担任委员会联合主席<ref>{{cite news |last=Roberts |first=Roxanne |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/trumps-inaugural-chairman-promises-a-celebration-of-harmony-inclusion-and-democracy/2016/12/06/51fb5e30-b8b0-11e6-b994-f45a208f7a73_story.html?utm_term=.52140dcac055&wpisrc=nl_rainbow&wpmm=1 |script-title=en:Trump inaugural chairman promises a celebration of ‘harmony, inclusion and democracy’ |work=The Washington Post |date=2016-12-06 |accessdate=2016-12-12 |archive-date=2017-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170131083827/https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/trumps-inaugural-chairman-promises-a-celebration-of-harmony-inclusion-and-democracy/2016/12/06/51fb5e30-b8b0-11e6-b994-f45a208f7a73_story.html?utm_term=.52140dcac055&wpisrc=nl_rainbow&wpmm=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。委员会成员包括赌场巨头[[谢尔登·阿德尔森|谢尔登·阿德尔森]]及其妻子米拉亚姆（{{lang|en|Miriam}}）、[[史提芬·艾伦·永利|史提芬·艾伦·永利]]和{{le|菲尔·拉芬|Phil Ruffin}}、石油大亨{{le|哈罗德·哈姆|Harold Hamm}}、女商人{{le|黛安·亨德里克斯|Diane Hendricks}}、煤炭大亨{{le|乔·克拉夫|Joe Craft}}、盖尔·戈尔登（{{lang|en|Gail Icahn}}）及其妻子[[卡尔·伊坎|卡尔·伊坎]]和[[纽约喷气机|纽约喷气机]]队老板{{le|伍迪·约翰逊|Woody Johnson}}<ref name="Comm">{{cite web|title=President-Elect Trump Announces Presidential Inaugural Committee Leadership|url=https://www.donaldjtrump.com/press-releases/president-elect-trump-announces-presidentialinaugural-committee-leader|website=www.donaldjtrump.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161227200140/https://www.donaldjtrump.com/press-releases/president-elect-trump-announces-presidentialinaugural-committee-leader|archivedate=2016-12-27|accessdate=2017-01-23}}</ref>。委员会报告称筹集到1亿多美元的就职典礼捐款<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/15/us/politics/trump-inauguration-donations-corporations.html|title=Corporations Open the Cash Spigot for Trump's Inauguration|work=The New York Times|date=2017-01-15|last=Fandos|first=Nicholas|accessdate=2017-01-23|archive-date=2017-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120171857/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/15/us/politics/trump-inauguration-donations-corporations.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

中華民國時任[[行政院长|行政院长]][[游锡堃|游锡堃]]率团代表[[中华民国总统|总统]][[蔡英文|蔡英文]]赴华盛顿特區参加就职典礼，遭到[[中華人民共和国外交部|中華人民共和国外交部]]抗议<ref>{{cite web|title=中国促美国阻止台湾代表出席新总统就职典礼|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/38663904|website=BBC中文网|accessdate=2017-01-23|date=2017-01-18|archive-date=2018-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615084535/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/38663904|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但代表团最终如期出席典礼<ref>{{cite web|author=郑仲岚|title=台湾代表团在中方抗议下参加特朗普就职典礼|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-38697270|website=BBC中文网|accessdate=2017-01-23|date=2017-01-17|archive-date=2018-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617121549/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-38697270|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，另有消息指[[鴻海|鴻海]]董事長[[郭台铭|郭台铭]]也受邀参加典礼，但他并不打算出席<ref>{{cite web|title=郭台铭受邀参加特朗普就职典礼但并不打算出席|url=http://news.sohu.com/20170119/n479084548.shtml|website=搜狐|accessdate=2017-01-23|date=2017-01-19|archive-date=2017-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170123082350/http://news.sohu.com/20170119/n479084548.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

