== 仪式前活动 ==
[[File:Donald_Trump_and_Melania_Trump_arrive_in_Washington_01-19-17.jpg|right]]
2017年1月17日，当选总统特朗普乘专机抵达华盛顿特区，出席题为“主席全球晚宴”（{{lang|en|Chairman's Global Dinner}}）的高规格晚宴，将即将上任的特朗普内阁官员介绍给各外国使节<ref name="hill">{{cite web |url=http://thehill.com/homenews/administration/314726-trump-lands-in-dc-for-pre-inauguration-dinner |title=Trump lands in DC for pre-inaugural dinner |publisher=The Hill |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-17 |author=Hensch, Mark |archive-date=2017-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120153102/http://thehill.com/homenews/administration/314726-trump-lands-in-dc-for-pre-inauguration-dinner |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》称晚宴是典礼前最高规格的活动，只能受邀参加，系黑色领带<ref name="wjglobal">{{cite web |url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/chairmans-global-dinner-most-exclusive-event-preceding-trump-inauguration-1484571781 |title=Chairman’s Global Dinner Most Exclusive Event Preceding Trump Inauguration |publisher=Wall Street Journal |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-17 |author=Bender, Michael |archive-date=2020-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812045849/https://www.wsj.com/articles/chairmans-global-dinner-most-exclusive-event-preceding-trump-inauguration-1484571781 |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，特朗普和彭斯在聚会中发表讲话。活动在[[安德鲁·梅隆礼堂|安德鲁·梅隆礼堂]]举行<ref name="hill"/>。就职活动主组织人托马斯·巴拉克（{{lang|en|Thomas Barrack}}）称晚宴“在社交民主及延伸全球大幕上刻下首枚指印”<ref name="hill"/>。經特朗普钦点继任[[约翰·克里|约翰·克里]]国务卿职位的[[雷克斯·蒂勒森|雷克斯·蒂勒森]]到場出席，另据在场记者观察，[[鲁迪·朱利安尼|鲁迪·朱利安尼]]、[[迈克尔·T·弗林|迈克尔·T·弗林]]和[[以色列駐美國大使館|以色列駐美國大使館]]{{le|罗德·德尔默|Ron Dermer}}亦在场<ref name="hill"/>。500名嘉宾中有200多名外交官<ref name="hill"/>。演讲中，特朗普自夸他迄今为止的内阁选择及选择迈克·彭斯位副总统<ref name="bg">{{cite news |url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/news/politics/2017/01/17/donald-trump-speaks-dinner-event/MttdAGSFF5ykboLhEiNF9H/story.html |title=Donald Trump speaks at dinner event in D.C. |publisher=The Boston Globe |agency=Associated Press |author=Reiss, Jaclyn |date=2017-01-17 |accessdate=2017-01-22 |archive-date=2017-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120211010/http://www.bostonglobe.com/news/politics/2017/01/17/donald-trump-speaks-dinner-event/MttdAGSFF5ykboLhEiNF9H/story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》和[[美联社|美联社]]披露菜单包括主菜芥菜黑鳕鱼和烤-{zh-hant:里; zh-hans:里;}-脊肉片，甜点有[[热烤阿拉斯加|热烤阿拉斯加]]<ref name="bg"/>。

[[File:Donald_Trump_and_Mike_Pence_wreath_laying_ceremony_01-19-17.jpg|left]]
1月19日，特朗普乘坐[[空军一号|空军一号]]从纽约市家中抵达华盛顿[[安德鲁斯联合基地|安德鲁斯联合基地]]<ref name="al">{{cite web |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/politics/articles/2017-01-19/trump-touches-down-in-washington-to-become-45th-u-s-president |title=Trump Era Dawns With Wreath-Laying and Reception Before Oath |publisher=Bloomberg |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-19 |author=Sink, Justin |archive-date=2017-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120075232/https://www.bloomberg.com/politics/articles/2017-01-19/trump-touches-down-in-washington-to-become-45th-u-s-president |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.al.com/news/index.ssf/2017/01/watch_president-elect_trump_me.html |title=Watch President-elect Trump, Melania Trump arrive in Washington, D.C. for Inauguration |publisher=AL.com |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-19 |author=Gore, Leada |archive-date=2017-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170909153809/http://www.al.com/news/index.ssf/2017/01/watch_president-elect_trump_me.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。离开纽约家前，特朗普发[[推特|推文]]：“准备离开前往华盛顿。旅途开始，我将非常努力地工作和奋斗，让这趟旅程对美国人民有意义。我认为，我们会毫无疑问地一起让美国再次强大<ref name="al"/>。”之后，特朗普在他于[[旧邮政局大厦|旧邮政局大厦]]建的酒店与彭斯用午餐<ref name="cbswr">{{cite web |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/donald-trump-arrives-in-washington-ahead-of-inauguration-day/ |title=Donald Trump arrives in Washington ahead of Inauguration Day |publisher=CBS News |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-19 |archive-date=2017-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170122142837/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/donald-trump-arrives-in-washington-ahead-of-inauguration-day/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之后前往[[阿灵顿国家公墓|阿灵顿国家公墓]]向[[无名烈士墓|无名烈士墓]]献花，家眷陪同<ref name="wreath">{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/01/19/politics/donald-trump-arlington-wreath/index.html |title=Donald Trump places wreath at Arlington |publisher=CNN |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-19 |author=Schleifer, Theodore |archive-date=2017-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121083657/http://www.cnn.com/2017/01/19/politics/donald-trump-arlington-wreath/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。巴拉克表示献花仪式是特朗普从候选人到总统的过渡<ref name="wreath"/>。布莱德利·贝克少将（{{lang|en|Major General Bradley Becker}}）陪同特朗普和彭斯出席仪式<ref name="cbswr"/>。阿灵顿国家公墓是40多万人的最终安息地，其中主要有[[美軍|美軍]]军人、荣誉勋章获得者和前总统[[约翰·肯尼迪|约翰·肯尼迪]]在内的高级政治官员<ref>{{cite web |url=http://patch.com/district-columbia/washingtondc/presidential-inauguration-2017-wreath-laying-ceremony-thursday |title=Watch Replay: Wreath-Laying Ceremony for Presidential Inauguration 2017 |publisher=Patch |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-19 |author=Barton, Mary Ann |archive-date=2017-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170122183529/http://patch.com/district-columbia/washingtondc/presidential-inauguration-2017-wreath-laying-ceremony-thursday |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

19日晚，特朗普主持为第二天观看就职典礼的支持者设置的名为“让美国再次伟大！欢迎庆祝活动”（{{lang|en|Make America Great Again! Welcome Celebration}}）音乐会。音乐会在[[林肯纪念堂|林肯纪念堂]]前台阶举行。多部音乐剧在音乐会上演出，[[李·格林伍德|李·格林伍德]]表演成名作之一《[[天佑美国_(李·格林伍德歌曲)|天佑美国]]》。{{le|托比·基斯|Toby Keith}}、{{le|三门关乐队|3 Doors Down}}和{{le|DJ·拉维德多姆斯|DJ Ravidrums}}也登台献唱<ref name="npr">{{cite web |url=http://www.npr.org/2017/01/19/510657291/trump-at-lincoln-memorial-concert-youre-not-forgotten-anymore |title=Trump At Lincoln Memorial Concert: 'You're Not Forgotten Anymore' |publisher=NPR |author=Taylor, Jessica |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-19 |archive-date=2017-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121105204/http://www.npr.org/2017/01/19/510657291/trump-at-lincoln-memorial-concert-youre-not-forgotten-anymore |dead-url=no }}</ref>。庆祝活动开始前，特朗普向支持者表示“被遗忘的男人和女人再也不会受到遗忘了”<ref name="npr"/>。演员[[强·沃特|强·沃特]]说：“我们见惯了一大堆让我们预感到不安的宣传，不知道上帝能否扭转所有针对这位唯一的愿望是让美国再次强大的特朗普先生的所有不利谣言<ref name="npr"/>。”音乐会在绚烂的焰火中结束<ref name="npr"/>。

[[File:U.S._Capitol_on_58th_Inauguration_Day_01-20-17.jpg|right]]正为就职典礼准备工作，太阳冉冉升起。]]
1月20日典礼当天早上，在靠近白宫的候任总统传统驻地[[布莱尔宫|布莱尔宫]]过夜后<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/onpolitics/2017/01/19/trumps-inauguration-eve-blair-house-stay-follows-inaugural-tradition/96800516/ |title=Trump's pre-inaugural Blair House stay follows presidential tradition |publisher=USA Today |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-20 |author=Korte, Gregory |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801202104/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/onpolitics/2017/01/19/trumps-inauguration-eve-blair-house-stay-follows-inaugural-tradition/96800516/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，特朗普和彭斯分别携夫人梅拉尼娅和卡伦参加{{le|圣约翰公会教堂|St. John's Episcopal Church, Lafayette Square}}的礼拜<ref name="time">{{cite news |url=http://time.com/4641208/donald-trump-robert-jeffress-st-john-episcopal-inauguration/ |title=Read the Sermon Donald Trump Heard Before Becoming President |publisher=Time Magazine |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-20 |archive-date=2017-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121143716/http://time.com/4641208/donald-trump-robert-jeffress-st-john-episcopal-inauguration/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该传统可追溯至[[詹姆斯·麦迪逊|詹姆斯·麦迪逊]]，自那时起每位总统都要在就职典礼当天早上参加礼拜<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/01/16/politics/inauguration-day-events-traditions/ |title=Presidents change, Inauguration Day stays the same |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-20 |author=Williams, Brenna |publisher=CNN |archive-date=2017-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170122023134/http://www.cnn.com/2017/01/16/politics/inauguration-day-events-traditions/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。礼拜由在竞选期间为特朗普宣传的[[美南浸信会|南方浸信会]]牧师{{le|罗伯特·杰弗斯|Robert Jeffress}}主持<ref name="time"/>。仪式后，特朗普和妻子到白宫会见总统[[巴拉克·奥巴马|巴拉克·奥巴马]]和[[米歇尔·奥巴马|米歇尔·奥巴马]]。奥巴马一家见过特朗普一家，梅拉尼娅向夫妇俩赠送礼物<ref name="tea">{{cite web |url=http://people.com/politics/presidential-inauguration-obamas-welcome-trumps-white-house-tea-coffee-meeting/ |title=The Obamas Welcome Donald and Melania Trump to the White House Just Before Inauguration |publisher=People |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-20 |author=McAfee, Tierney |archive-date=2017-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170122001902/http://people.com/politics/presidential-inauguration-obamas-welcome-trumps-white-house-tea-coffee-meeting/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之后白宫记者团为他们拍摄合影<ref name="tea"/>。赠送礼物是米歇尔开始的传统，她曾在2009年丈夫就职典礼当日向[[乔治·布什|乔治·布什]]和[[劳拉·布什|劳拉·布什]]送礼物<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/melania-trump-gifts-michelle-obama-blue-tiffany-box-watch-w462077 |title=Melania Trump Gifts Michelle Obama a Blue Tiffany Box: Watch Her Reaction |publisher=Us Magazine |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-20 |author=Blynn, Jamie |archive-date=2017-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170122121049/http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/melania-trump-gifts-michelle-obama-blue-tiffany-box-watch-w462077 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之后，他们在白宫内举行茶话会，[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]和彭斯分别携妻子[[吉尔·拜登|吉尔·拜登]]和[[凯伦·彭斯|凯伦·彭斯]]陪同<ref name="tea"/>。依照传统，总统与当选总统会晤后，会共同乘坐总统车队豪华轿车前往国会大厦就职典礼<ref name="tea"/>。

