上午11时41分，[[罗伊·布伦特|罗伊·布伦特]]揭开典礼序幕。他在开场白中提到国家有着“平淡、奇迹般”的权力和平过渡历史。随后三个宗教团体[[祷告|祷告]]，紧接着[[密苏里州立大学|密苏里州立大学]]合唱队表演原创作品《Now We Belong》。简短发言后，[[查克·舒默|查克·舒默]]在演讲最后让所有人宣誓仪式中起立<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/2017/live-updates/politics/live-coverage-of-trumps-inauguration/president-elect-donald-trump-introduced-blunt-kicks-off-ceremony/|script-title=en:Blunt kicks off ‘commonplace and miraculous’ transfer of power|work=Washington Post|date=2016-01-20|accessdate=2016-01-21|archive-date=2017-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170130152540/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/2017/live-updates/politics/live-coverage-of-trumps-inauguration/president-elect-donald-trump-introduced-blunt-kicks-off-ceremony/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#1">{{cite news|url=http://www1.cbn.com/cbnnews/2017/january/unprecedented-prayer-on-display-at-trump-inauguration|title=Unprecedented Prayer on Display at Trump Inauguration|work=CBN News|date=2016-01-21|accessdate=2016-01-21|archive-date=2017-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121154529/http://www1.cbn.com/cbnnews/2017/january/unprecedented-prayer-on-display-at-trump-inauguration|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2017/01/20/politics/missouri-state-chorale-now-we-belong-lyrics/|title=Missouri State Chorale performs 'Now We Belong' at inauguration|work=CNN|date=2016-01-20|accessdate=2016-01-21|archive-date=2017-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170128204915/http://edition.cnn.com/2017/01/20/politics/missouri-state-chorale-now-we-belong-lyrics/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2017/01/20/politics/sen-chuck-schumer-inauguration-speech/|title=Sen. Chuck Schumer delivers remarks at Trump inauguration ceremony|work=CNN|date=2016-01-20|accessdate=2016-01-21|archive-date=2017-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170128224319/http://edition.cnn.com/2017/01/20/politics/sen-chuck-schumer-inauguration-speech/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[美国总统|前总统]][[吉米·卡特|吉米·卡特]]、[[比尔·克林顿|比尔·克林顿]]、[[喬治·W·布希|喬治·W·布希]]及[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]均携[[美国第一夫人|第一夫人]]出席典礼<ref>{{cite news|last=Jackson|first=David M.|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/onpolitics/2017/01/03/donald-trump-hillary-clinton-bill-clinton-inauguration/96117260|title=Hillary Clinton, Bill Clinton, George W. Bush to attend Trump inauguration|work=USA Today|date=2017-01-03|accessdate=2017-01-03|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104155006/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/onpolitics/2017/01/03/donald-trump-hillary-clinton-bill-clinton-inauguration/96117260/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中包括特朗普竞选中的主要竞争对手[[希拉里·克林顿|希拉里·克林顿]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/01/03/politics/george-w-bush-laura-bush-to-attend-trump-inauguration/index.html|title=Bill, Hillary Clinton to attend Trump Inauguration|last=CNN|first=Dan Merica and Theodore Schleifer|website=CNN|access-date=2017-01-15|archive-date=2017-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116173710/http://www.cnn.com/2017/01/03/politics/george-w-bush-laura-bush-to-attend-trump-inauguration/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[乔治·赫伯特·沃克·布什|乔治·赫伯特·沃克·布什]]及妻子[[芭芭拉·布什|芭芭拉·布什]]因身体抱恙缺席典礼<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.kbtx.com/content/news/George-HW-Bush-Barbara-will-not-attend-Trump-inauguration-409577605.html|title=George H.W. Bush, Barbara will not attend Trump inauguration|last=Fullhart|first=Steve|access-date=2017-01-15|archive-date=2017-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118061000/http://www.kbtx.com/content/news/George-HW-Bush-Barbara-will-not-attend-Trump-inauguration-409577605.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[美国副总统|前副总统]][[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]<ref>{{cite web|last=McAfee|first=Tierney|title=Donald Trump Is Sworn In as the 45th President of the United States|url=http://people.com/politics/presidential-inauguration-donald-trump-sworn-in-45th-president-united-states/|website=People|accessdate=2017-01-21|date=2017-01-20|archive-date=2017-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121015331/http://people.com/politics/presidential-inauguration-donald-trump-sworn-in-45th-president-united-states/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[丹·奎尔|丹·奎尔]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.indystar.com/story/news/2017/01/20/live-scenes-trump-pence-inauguration-day/96808288/ |title=Live: Scenes from Trump-Pence Inauguration Day |publisher=Indianapolis Star |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-20 |author=Cook, Tony |archive-date=2017-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170909153809/http://www.indystar.com/story/news/2017/01/20/live-scenes-trump-pence-inauguration-day/96808288/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[迪克·切尼|迪克·切尼]]<ref>{{cite news|title=The many faces at Donald Trump's inauguration|url=http://nypost.com/2017/01/20/the-many-faces-at-donald-trumps-inauguration/#12|accessdate=2017-01-21|work=New York Post|date=2017-01-20|archive-date=2017-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170122153342/http://nypost.com/2017/01/20/the-many-faces-at-donald-trumps-inauguration/#12|dead-url=no}}</ref>均在场。

11时54分，[[美国最高法院大法官|最高法院大法官]][[克拉伦斯·托马斯|克拉伦斯·托马斯]]监督迈克·彭斯宣誓成为第48任[[美国副总统|美国副总统]]，此时彭斯手按自己的和[[罗纳德·里根|罗纳德·里根]]的《圣经》，而里根激发了彭斯加入[[共和党_(美国)|共和党]]的想法。{{le|摩门合唱团|Mormon Tabernacle Choir}}演唱《[[美丽的阿美利加|美丽的阿美利加]]》后，[[美国首席大法官|首席法官]][[约翰·罗伯茨|约翰·罗伯茨]]监督特朗普宣誓就任第45任美国总统。特朗普在宣誓中用了两本《圣经》，一本是她母亲赠予的，一本是[[林肯圣经|林肯遗留的]]。仪式后，[[美国海军陆战队军乐团|海军陆战队军乐团]]演唱进行曲《[[向统帅致敬|向统帅致敬]]》，同时{{le|21响礼炮|21-gun salute}}鸣放<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2017/01/19/mike-pence-vice-president-swearing-in-symbolism/96782426/|title=Mike Pence's swearing-in is full of symbolism|work=USA Today|date=2017-01-19|last=Groppe|first=Maureen|accessdate=2017-01-21|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023092038/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2017/01/19/mike-pence-vice-president-swearing-in-symbolism/96782426/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/01/20/politics/inauguration-live-coverage/index.html|title=Trump inauguration: Live coverage|work=CNN|date=2017-01-21|author=Daniella Diaz, Sophie Tatum, Amanda Wills and Alysha Love, CNN|accessdate=2017-01-21|archive-date=2017-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120235847/http://www.cnn.com/2017/01/20/politics/inauguration-live-coverage/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#2">{{cite news|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/expect-donald-trumps-inauguration/story?id=44737678|title=The Tick-Tock of Donald Trump's Inauguration|work=ABC News|date=2017-01-19|last=Stracqualursi|first=Veronica|accessdate=2017-01-21|archive-date=2017-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121153048/http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/expect-donald-trumps-inauguration/story?id=44737678|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2017/01/18/the-symbolism-of-trumps-two-inaugural-bible-choices-from-lincoln-to-his-mother/|title=The symbolism of Trump’s two inaugural Bible choices, from Lincoln to his mother|work=Washington Post|date=2017-01-18|last=Stracqualursi|first=Veronica|accessdate=2017-01-21|archive-date=2017-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121003555/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2017/01/18/the-symbolism-of-trumps-two-inaugural-bible-choices-from-lincoln-to-his-mother/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

特朗普随后发表长达16分钟的就职演说，共计1433字，是自卡特{{le|1977年美国总统就职典礼|Inauguration of Jimmy Carter|1977年}}1229字就职演说以来最短的。演说后，三大宗教（猶太教、天主教、基督新教）领导人轮番{{le|祝祷|Benediction}}，使典礼的祈祷次数创下了六次的历史新高。[[葛福临|葛福临]]牧师、[[天主教纽约总教区|天主教纽约总教区]]总主教[[蒂莫西·麦可·多兰|蒂莫西·麦可·多兰]]、{{le|塞缪尔·罗德里格兹|Samuel Rodriguez}}、[[宝拉·怀特|宝拉·怀特]]牧师、犹太教教士{{le|马文·希尔|Marvin Hier}}和韦恩·T·杰克逊（{{lang|en|Wayne T. Jackson}}）主教轮番祝祷。典礼在[[贾姬·伊凡柯|贾姬·伊凡柯]]演唱[[星条旗永不落|国歌]]声中落幕<ref>{{cite news|url=https://nypost.com/2017/01/20/trumps-inauguration-speech-was-really-really-short/|title=Trump’s inauguration speech was really, really short|work=New York Post|date=2017-01-20|last=Italiano|first=Laura|accessdate=2017-01-21|archive-date=2017-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120195942/http://nypost.com/2017/01/20/trumps-inauguration-speech-was-really-really-short/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2017/01/20/us/politics/donald-trump-inauguration-speech-transcript.html|work=The New York Times|date=2017-01-20|last=|first=|accessdate=2017-01-21|title=Donald Trump’s Inaugural Speech, Annotated|archive-date=2020-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200301120526/https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2017/01/20/us/politics/donald-trump-inauguration-speech-transcript.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2017/01/trump-inaugural-speech-analysis/513956/|title='America First': Donald Trump's Populist Inaugural Address|work=The Atlantic|date=2017-01-20|last=Graham|first=David|accessdate=2017-01-21|archive-date=2017-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121003122/https://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2017/01/trump-inaugural-speech-analysis/513956/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#1"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/inauguration/7662486/jackie-evancho-national-anthem-performance-donald-trump-inauguration-video|title=Watch Jackie Evancho Deliver the National Anthem at Donald Trump's Inauguration|work=Billboard (magazine)|date=2016-01-20|accessdate=2016-01-21|archive-date=2017-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121101923/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/inauguration/7662486/jackie-evancho-national-anthem-performance-donald-trump-inauguration-video|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

宣誓仪式后，特朗普与奥巴马一家前往传统告别仪式。仪式中，前第一家庭登上直升机前往[[安德鲁斯联合基地|安德鲁斯联合基地]]。在直升机前，特朗普一家与奥巴马一家短暂交谈后，退回国会台阶处，挥手目送直升机离去。片刻后，特朗普到[[椭圆形办公室|椭圆形办公室]]签署上任后首个行政命令，其中包括启动废除[[奥巴马医改|奥巴马医改]]程序的命令<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.politico.com/story/2017/01/trump-inauguration-five-things-to-watch-233885|title=Trump sworn in as 45th president|work=Politico|date=2016-01-20|accessdate=2016-01-21|author=Louis Nelson, Madeline Conway and Eli Stokols|archive-date=2017-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121003902/http://www.politico.com/story/2017/01/trump-inauguration-five-things-to-watch-233885|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-trump-executiveorder-idUSKBN155010|title=Trump, in Oval Office, signs first order on Obamacare|work=Reuters|date=2016-01-21|accessdate=2016-01-21|author=Jeff Mason and Roberta Rampton|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112043544/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-trump-executiveorder-idUSKBN155010|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

特朗普、彭斯携妻子与国会领袖及其他議員在{{le|国家雕像馆|National Statuary Hall}}就餐。用餐过后，特朗普让与餐者起立鼓掌致敬他的选战对手希拉里·克林顿<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rollcall.com/news/hoh/statuary-lunch-hall-model-make-nice-decorum|title=Statuary Lunch Hall a Model of Make-Nice Decorum|work=Roll Call|date=2016-01-20|accessdate=2016-01-21|author=John T. Bennett|archive-date=2017-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170129015838/http://www.rollcall.com/news/hoh/statuary-lunch-hall-model-make-nice-decorum|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://qz.com/888791/trump-and-pence-are-receiving-official-inauguration-gifts-from-the-american-people/|title=Trump and Pence are receiving official inauguration gifts from "the American people"|work=Quartz (publication)|date=2016-01-20|accessdate=2016-01-21|author=Zameena Mejia|archive-date=2017-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170130071529/https://qz.com/888791/trump-and-pence-are-receiving-official-inauguration-gifts-from-the-american-people/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.politico.com/story/2017/01/2017-trump-inauguration-clintons-233929|title=Hillary Clinton gets standing ovation at Trump luncheon|work=Politico|date=2016-01-20|accessdate=2016-01-21|author=Louis Nelson|archive-date=2017-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170120232722/http://www.politico.com/story/2017/01/2017-trump-inauguration-clintons-233929|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

作为[[美军|美军]]新[[总司令|总司令]]，特朗普在国会大厦东翼检阅军队各部队代表，之后参加游行。游行结束后，特朗普的一天以出席华盛顿三大舞会结束<ref name="#2"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/2017/01/21/510917522/photos-trump-ends-inauguration-day-his-way-with-dances-at-3-balls|title=PHOTOS: Trump Ends Inauguration Day His Way, With Dances At 3 Balls|publisher=NPR|accessdate=2017-01-22|archive-date=2017-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121232857/http://www.npr.org/2017/01/21/510917522/photos-trump-ends-inauguration-day-his-way-with-dances-at-3-balls|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 现场人数 ==
典礼前夕，联邦和地方部门预估到场人数在70万到90万之间<ref>{{cite news|url=http://europe.newsweek.com/trump-inauguration-numbers-how-many-attended-545467?rm=eu|title=Inauguration and Women’s March, By The Numbers|work=Newsweek|date=2017-01-21|accessdate=2017-01-22|last=Kutner|first=Max|archive-date=2017-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170123182234/http://europe.newsweek.com/trump-inauguration-numbers-how-many-attended-545467?rm=eu|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcwashington.com/news/local/Trump-Inauguration-Crowd-Estimates-410559995.html|title=How Many People Will Attend Trump's Inauguration? Why to Take Turnout Estimates With a Grain of Salt|publisher=NBC|date=2017-01-13|accessdate=2017-01-22|last=Swalec|first=Andrea|archive-date=2017-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170122115004/http://www.nbcwashington.com/news/local/Trump-Inauguration-Crowd-Estimates-410559995.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》援引英国曼彻斯特城市大学的[[公众科学|公众科学]]Keith Still教授的分析认为，周五出现在国家广场的人群规模约为奥巴马当年的三分之一。<ref name="nyt average">{{cite news|last1=Wallace|first1=Tim|last2=Parlapiano|first2=Alicia|title=Crowd Scientists Say Women's March in Washington Had 3 Times More People Than Trump's Inauguration|url=https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2017/01/22/us/politics/womens-march-trump-crowd-estimates.html|accessdate=2017-01-22|work=纽约时报|date=2017-01-22|archive-date=2017-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313210125/https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2017/01/22/us/politics/womens-march-trump-crowd-estimates.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[今日美國|今日美國]]报道说游行路线上有"数量可观"的空位。<ref>{{cite web|author=William Cummings|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/onpolitics/2017/01/20/inaugural-parade-crowd-size/96855252/|title=There were a lot of empty seats in the stands along Trump's parade route|newspaper=USA Today|accessdate=2017-01-22|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128165130/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/onpolitics/2017/01/20/inaugural-parade-crowd-size/96855252/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 多家媒体登载了2009年奥巴马总统宣誓就职仪式与特朗普就职典礼的同角度航拍对比图，暗示参加特朗普就职典礼的人群规模远小于前总统奥巴马。<ref name="telegraph-crowd" />上届奥巴马[[2009年美国总统就职典礼|2009年的就职典礼]]估计有180万人观礼<ref name="telegraph-crowd">{{cite web|last1=Millward|first1=David|title=Trump inauguration turnout dwarfed by Obama in 2009|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/01/20/trump-inauguration-turnout-dwarfed-obama-2009/|website=每日电讯报|accessdate=2017-01-22|archive-date=2018-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181117040646/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/01/20/trump-inauguration-turnout-dwarfed-obama-2009/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，一时创下[[国家广场|国家广场]]的人数数目记录<ref name="Ranked">{{cite web | last1=Gillin | first1=John | title=Inaugural Crowd Sizes Ranked | url=http://www.politifact.com/truth-o-meter/article/2017/jan/20/inaugural-crowd-sizes-ranked/ | date=2017-01-20 | publisher=PolitiFact.com | accessdate=2017-01-21 | archive-date=2019-02-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190227043336/https://www.politifact.com/truth-o-meter/article/2017/jan/20/inaugural-crowd-sizes-ranked/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。据[[AC尼尔森|AC尼尔森]]的调查报告显示， 当天通过媒体收看特朗普就职典礼的观众人数为3060万，高于2013年奥巴马第二次就职典礼2060万的观众人数，但低于2009年奥巴马初次就职典礼时 3780万的观众人数。<ref name="nyt inaugfacts">{{cite news|last=Fandos|first=Nicholas|title=White House Pushes 'Alternative Facts.' Here Are the Real Ones.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/22/us/politics/president-trump-inauguration-crowd-white-house.html|work=纽约时报|date=2017-01-22|accessdate=2017-01-25|archive-date=2017-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170123000019/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/22/us/politics/president-trump-inauguration-crowd-white-house.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>有政治分析师指出由于奥巴马身为首位非裔美国人总统这一性质才是造成差异的成因<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/photos-president-trumps-inauguration-crowd-vs-president-obamas/ |title=President Trump's inauguration crowd was smaller than Obama's |publisher=CBS News |author=Adams, Cydney |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-20 |archive-date=2019-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190428052352/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/photos-president-trumps-inauguration-crowd-vs-president-obamas/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/donald-trump-inauguration-attendance_us_588238c7e4b070d8cad20a0d |title=The National Mall Looked Relatively Empty For Donald Trump’s Inauguration |publisher=赫芬顿邮报 |accessdate=2017-01-22 |date=2017-01-20 |author=Reilly, Mollie |archive-date=2018-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181207200545/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/donald-trump-inauguration-attendance_us_588238c7e4b070d8cad20a0d |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

